```
<div class="section">
  <div class="s-head">
    <span class="s-num">01</span>
    <span class="s-title">Background — The Need</span>
  </div>
  <p>Online commerce is broken for the AI era. Products are discovered in videos, AI chats, and voice assistants — but buying requires leaving that surface entirely. Merchants need custom integrations for every new AI touchpoint, costing weeks and thousands of dollars per surface.</p>
  <div class="pill-row">
    <span class="pill red">No in-context buying</span>
    <span class="pill red">Fragmented checkout</span>
    <span class="pill red">Custom integrations per surface</span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="hr"></div>

<div class="section">
  <div class="s-head">
    <span class="s-num">02</span>
    <span class="s-title">Problem Statement</span>
  </div>
  <ul>
    <li>AI agents cannot transact directly with existing stores — every surface needs a new custom build</li>
    <li>Products seen in videos cannot be purchased in context — buyers drop off navigating away</li>
    <li>Price-sensitive buyers have no autonomous, hands-free way to act on price drops</li>
    <li>Merchant onboarding to new AI surfaces takes 2–4 weeks and costs $10K–$50K per integration</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="hr"></div>

<div class="section">
  <div class="s-head">
    <span class="s-num">03</span>
    <span class="s-title">Solution &amp; AI Stack</span>
  </div>
  <p>ShopLens is a multi-merchant agentic commerce platform built on Google's <strong>Universal Commerce Protocol (UCP)</strong>. Any merchant registers once — their products become instantly purchasable through AI agents, shoppable video, and autonomous price-triggered buying.</p>
  <div class="chip-row">
    <span class="chip hi">UCP Protocol</span>
    <span class="chip">YOLOv8</span>
    <span class="chip">CLIP + ChromaDB</span>
    <span class="chip">LangChain + Ollama</span>
    <span class="chip">FastAPI</span>
    <span class="chip">Celery + Redis</span>
    <span class="chip">Next.js</span>
    <span class="chip hi">SingleStore</span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="hr"></div>

<div class="section">
  <div class="s-head">
    <span class="s-num">05</span>
    <span class="s-title">Why AI Only</span>
  </div>
  <div class="why-box">
    <p><strong>Object detection</strong> — YOLOv8 identifies shoppable products in real-time video frames. No human can review every frame at scale.<br/><br/>
    <strong>Semantic matching</strong> — CLIP bridges the gap between "what the camera sees" and "what the merchant sells" using embeddings, not keyword lookup.<br/><br/>
    <strong>Conversational intent</strong> — LLM understands multi-turn shopping dialogue, extracts price thresholds, and resolves ambiguous references like "buy this one".<br/><br/>
    <strong>Autonomous purchasing</strong> — Celery agent monitors prices 24/7 and executes checkout without human intervention when conditions are met.</p>
  </div>
</div>
