<div class="uc-card uc1">
  <div class="uc-num">USE CASE 01</div>
  <div class="uc-title">In-Video Commerce — See It, Buy It</div>
  <p>User watches a product video. AI scans frames via YOLOv8, matches detected objects to merchant catalog using CLIP embeddings, and surfaces a shoppable overlay. One tap fires a UCP checkout via SingleStore's Single Checkout — order placed without leaving the video.</p>
  <div class="uc-flow">
    <span class="uc-step">Watch video</span>
    <span class="uc-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="uc-step">Scan frame</span>
    <span class="uc-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="uc-step">AI detects product</span>
    <span class="uc-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="uc-step">Overlay appears</span>
    <span class="uc-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="uc-step">Buy Now → Order placed</span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="uc-card uc2">
  <div class="uc-num">USE CASE 02</div>
  <div class="uc-title">Autonomous Price-Drop Buying</div>
  <p>User tells the AI agent via chat or voice: <em>"Reserve this headphone — buy it when it drops below $150."</em> LLM extracts intent and threshold. Celery worker polls UCP catalog every minute across all merchants. When price drops, checkout fires automatically — buyer just gets notified.</p>
  <div class="uc-flow">
    <span class="uc-step">Chat: "Buy below $150"</span>
    <span class="uc-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="uc-step">LLM extracts threshold</span>
